headline: The Bull Case For DoorDash (DASH) Could Change Following New Partnerships in Hardware, Beauty, and Business
summary: In September 2025, DoorDash secured several new partnerships, including exclusive overnight delivery with Waffle House, a national rollout with Ace Hardware, a promotional pop-up collaboration with Sally Beauty in New York City, and an employee perk alliance with Brex to offer DashPass memberships to business users. These high-profile collaborations highlight DoorDash's expansion into new verticals and customer segments, underscoring its drive to broaden beyond its core restaurant delivery...

headline: These 5 Side Hustles Are On Their Way Out In the Trump Economy
summary: Side hustles are a popular way to make extra cash. According to MarketWatch, 51% of Americans had a side hustle in 2024. But the industry is changing.
